{"tid":257306,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被指巴士上屢侵犯女律政書記     250磅銀行經理辯稱座位太窄","createTime":"2017-05-25T07:23:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-25T07:29:08.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eefb672fcd68071f94beed18ec165d397e396ccd","tid":257306,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T07:23:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170525/large/1495695372_e2bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170525%2Flarge%2F1495695372_e2bb.jpg&h=1af934ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n高大健壯、體重達250磅的銀行經理，涉9日內兩度在巴士上對同一名女律政書記上下其手，數度用手肘碰撞對方乳房及摸大腿。經理被控非禮罪，案件今續審時，經理自辯稱巴士座位狹窄，以往試過意外觸碰乘客，巴士全程亦有很多急彎。但對於事主指他於去年2月23日及3月3日數次摸她的大腿及以手肘撞其乳房，他則稱沒有印象。<br />\n<br />\n34歲被告潘君諾作供時透露，他於2004年於本地大學畢業，當時修讀金融服務，畢業後在同一家銀行工作至今，負責管理其中一間分行。被告又稱他已婚，與妻子育有兩子。"},{"pid":"17b4e43b8fcf232c4204e84d093e4a2158f42f1a","tid":257306,"uid":8000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T07:24:29.000Z","msg":"又係飛影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e94b308139e27d45d6bbbfbbd4b4ca688b6e903","tid":257306,"uid":85586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T07:26:08.000Z","msg":"肥毒撚fat fat<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65a0f82b920877ddd2679de0386f73a41bf2c1b4","tid":257306,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T07:27:42.000Z","msg":"識食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afa8c5c6084db87f52a6bf016fdeb0e76d28496f","tid":257306,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T07:29:08.000Z","msg":"搭巴士真係見過d仆街明明可以無身體接觸都要迫埋黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}